We the people contributing to, discussing and/or otherwise engaging with the repository or content contained within it abide by the code of conduct detailed hereafter.

0. I will use common sense in my interpretation of this code of conduct. I will consider the mantra of "do as you would be done by".
1. I will respect others and their fundamental rights to their opinions and identities.
2. I will not use any characteristic of a person against them as an insult. This includes but is not limited to:
2a. their skin color, ethnicity or nationality,
2b. their age, education or status,
2c. their sexual orientation or identity, gender or sex,
2d. their expression of themselves and their appearance.
3. I will foster trust and empathy.
4. I will not attack others in ways that include but are not limited to:
4a. publicly or privately harassing them,
4b. doxxing them.
